 	<div id="main-article-info">
 		
					
				
			<h1
																									>Afghanistan war logs: the unvarnished picture</h1>
				
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"																				>A leaked trove of US military logs reveals a very different landscape from the one with which we have become familiar</p>
		
				
  	</div>
  	
